4. Tim Draper: Bitcoin can hedge against excessive US government spending and is optimistic about reaching $250,000 this year;
5. Trend Research once again withdrew 4,000 ETH from the exchange, and the current total value of holdings exceeds $347 million;
6. Binance Alpha launched AB (AB), and users with at least 225 points can receive 9,882 AB airdrops;
7. Mempool: No so-called encryption recovery service is provided, beware of phishing email scams;
8. Data: USDC circulation has increased by about 100 million in the past 7 days;
9. Analyst: If the market resumes its short-term bullish momentum, it needs to close at Above $104,800;
10. Farcaster will airdrop limited edition NFTs to the first 10,000 Pro subscribers next week.
